select today.id from weather yesterday cross join weather today where DATEDIFF(today.recordDate,yesterDay.recordDate)=1 and today.temperature>yesterday.temperature;

step by step explaination:

Since we eed to finnd a day that is hotter than the previous day we will be creating all the possible combbinations of the rows of the same table.

Thus we will be using cartesian product (CROSS product). 

the we will be narrowing it down to the pair of consecutive days(using DATEDIFF),

